      <talk_question mid="9"><![CDATA[<html>$高级牧师杰梅因$<BR><FONT color=#a82424>死亡森林</FONT>的事办得如何了?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n034_cleric_master_germain-accepting-a" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n034_cleric_master_germain-accepting-b" mid="18"><![CDATA[<html>(继续)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="17"><![CDATA[<html>$高级牧师杰梅因$<BR>还好。我的老师也可以安息了。</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
