   <talk_paragraph index="n034_cleric_master_germain-1" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n034_cleric_master_germain-1-a" mid="24"><![CDATA[<html>嗯，那个雷安的妻子现在怎么样了?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="23"><![CDATA[<html>$高级牧师杰梅因$<BR>如果死亡森林的毒气没有污染她的灵魂的话，一定会在女神的怀抱中安息了吧。</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n034_cleric_master_germain-1-a" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n034_cleric_master_germain-1-b" mid="26"><![CDATA[<html>这事可真奇怪啊。</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="25"><![CDATA[<html>$高级牧师杰梅因$<BR>是啊，10年离开这个村庄后，就再也没有听说过<FONT color=#a82424>克拉拉</FONT>这个女子的消息呢。嗯，这样看来，在这10年当中她似乎也再也没有回到这里。</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n034_cleric_master_germain-1-b" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n034_cleric_master_germain-1-c" mid="28"><![CDATA[<html>那么就不知道她们去哪里了吗？</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="27"><![CDATA[<html>$高级牧师杰梅因$<BR>是啊，嗯，为了把那些遗物交给她们母女俩，怎么也得找找她们看看吧?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n034_cleric_master_germain-1-c" image="QW_PrairieTown.dds" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n034_cleric_master_germain-1-d" mid="30"><![CDATA[<html>那么到普雷利镇应该能获得一些关于母女俩的线索吧。</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="29"><![CDATA[<html>$高级牧师杰梅因$<BR>根据日志，雷安说自己的妻子和女儿避难去了西方。 在凯德拉西部最近的村庄就是 <FONT color=#a82424>普雷利镇</FONT>。</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n034_cleric_master_germain-1-d" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n034_cleric_master_germain-2" mid="32"><![CDATA[<html>嗯，那我就去一趟普雷利镇吧。</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="31"><![CDATA[<html>$高级牧师杰梅因$<BR>真是麻烦你了，就烦劳您去打听一下她们的消息并把遗物交给她们吧。我因为这里不断增加伤员，无法抽身离开 凯德拉呢。</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n204_grave_of_clara-1" image="QN_TombStone01.dds" itemindex="">
      <talk_question mid="87"><![CDATA[<html>$克拉拉的坟墓$<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>雷安深爱着的爱人，亦是箩丝慈祥而又勇敢的母亲。<BR>善良而又美丽的克拉拉，在这里沉睡着。</FONT> </html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n001_elder_harold-1" image="QN_Npc_Cl_master_Germain.dds" itemindex="">
      <talk_question mid="88"><![CDATA[<html>$村长海洛德$<BR>欢迎来到我们的村庄。我们这里虽说不上富足，但还是可以满足你的基本所需的。<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>（要彻底完成凯德拉关卡的高级牧师杰梅因之间的对话）</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n034_cleric_master_germain-2" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_question mid="38"><![CDATA[<html>$高级牧师杰梅因$<BR><FONT color=#a82424>普雷利镇</FONT>的事，这里的村长<FONT color=#a82424>海洛德</FONT>大人应该最了解了。<BR>不妨先找他打听一下吧。우</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n001_elder_harold-2" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n001_elder_harold-2-check" mid="40"><![CDATA[<html>(继续)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="39"><![CDATA[<html>$村长海洛德$<BR>呼，<FONT color=#a82424>箩丝</FONT>不知道现在怎么样了...<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>（村长担心的叹了一口气）</FONT> </html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n001_elder_harold-2-a" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n001_elder_harold-2-b" mid="42"><![CDATA[<html>为了询问10年前来到这里的母女相关的事而来找您的。</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="41"><![CDATA[<html>$村长海洛德$<BR>哦，欢迎。找我有什么事吗?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n001_elder_harold-2-b" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n001_elder_harold-2-c" mid="44"><![CDATA[<html>为了转达雷安的遗物。</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="43"><![CDATA[<html>$村长海洛德$<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>（村长海洛德充满警惕的眼神）</FONT><BR>为何问那种事情啊?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n001_elder_harold-2-c" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n001_elder_harold-2-d" mid="46"><![CDATA[<html>（海洛德似乎以悔恨的眼神望着天空）</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="45"><![CDATA[<html>$村长海洛德$<BR><FONT color=#a82424>雷安</FONT>... 那个人最终还是死去了啊。就如你所说，10年前确实有对母女到过这里。</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n001_elder_harold-2-d" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n001_elder_harold-2-e" mid="48"><![CDATA[<html>(继续)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="47"><![CDATA[<html>$村长海洛德$<BR>她叫<FONT color=#a82424>克拉拉</FONT>，来的时候已经是奄奄一息了。因为逃亡时被魔物们追杀而受了重伤。临死前她把自己的女儿托付给了我。</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n001_elder_harold-2-e" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n001_elder_harold-2-f" mid="50"><![CDATA[<html>那个女儿怎么样了?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="49"><![CDATA[<html>$村长海洛德$<BR>她拖着受到重伤的身体走出村外，把魔物们吸引到了其他地方。最后在离村庄十分遥远的绝壁跳下自杀而死。无疑克拉拉是想保护村庄和女儿。</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n001_elder_harold-2-f" image="QN_Rose.dds" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n001_elder_harold-2-g" mid="53"><![CDATA[<html>哦? 那个叫箩丝的少女就是那对夫妇的女儿吗?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="51"><![CDATA[<html>$村长海洛德$<BR>那个女儿... <FONT color=#a82424>箩丝</FONT>的名字是我给我的孙女取的。本想让她平凡的过完幸福的一生，这个要求很过分吗。</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n001_elder_harold-2-g" image="QN_Rose.dds" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n001_elder_harold-2-h" mid="55"><![CDATA[<html>叫克拉拉的那个女子尸体是怎么处理的?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="54"><![CDATA[<html>$村长海洛德$<BR>是啊，被称为<FONT color=#a82424>先知者</FONT>的那个可怜的孩子就是他们夫妇的女儿。而且那个孩子早已不在此地，这些遗物没人能接受啊?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n001_elder_harold-2-h" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n001_elder_harold-2-i" mid="57"><![CDATA[<html>墓地在哪里?我想把遗物放在那里。</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="56"><![CDATA[<html>$村长海洛德$<BR>在绝壁下找到尸体后，我们葬在了村庄墓地当中。曾经研究古代人的时候，偶然还碰到过那对夫妇。因此对于有一面之缘的那对夫妇，我总不能撒手不管啊。</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n001_elder_harold-2-i" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n001_elder_harold-3" mid="59"><![CDATA[<html>知道了。</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="58"><![CDATA[<html>$村长海洛德$<BR>也是…既然没有人能接收遗物，不妨就献给她的墓地上吧。去那边的<FONT color=#a82424>坟墓</FONT>看看吧。</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n001_elder_harold-2-j" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n001_elder_harold-2-b" mid="90"><![CDATA[<html>为了询问10年前来到这里的母女相关的事而来找您的。</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="89"><![CDATA[<html>$村长海洛德$<BR>
啊，<FONT color=#382000>{user_nick}</FONT>不对啊，怎么又回来了?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n001_elder_harold-3" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_question mid="60"><![CDATA[<html>$村长海洛德$<BR>他们一家也够凄惨的。就因为继承了所谓<FONT color=#a82424> 古代人的血统</FONT>而要遭此劫难... 咳咳... 早知如此就该把箩丝交付给神圣天堂教堂了啊。</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
